    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "That's interesting. Can you go deeper into why Profile B's background would be viewed as an aggravating factor? Usually, \"systemic disadvantage\" sounds like it should be a mitigating factor, right? Why would it actually lead to a harsher sentence?",
